      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic repairs to be fully functional. The engine currently runs very roughly and likely needs a complete overhaul, and the transmission exhibits significant slipping. Body-wise, there is noticeable rust on the wheel wells and several large dents on the passenger side. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn seating and a non-functional climate control system. This car is ideal for a mechanic looking for a project or as a donor for parts.",
