    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 power plant, delivering 333hp via individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain provides a visceral, mechanical connection. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane subframe bushings, addressing common floor pan fatigue issues. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS system refresh and valve clearance adjustment to ensure optimal timing and compression. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the suspension geometry is dialed in with Bilstein B16 coilovers, and the variable M differential lock ensures precise torque distribution during corner exit. A driver-centric example ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
