    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2018 Lexus RX 350 in Atomic Silver, a vehicle that perfectly balances luxury with everyday utility. This SUV has been maintained with a high level of care, evidenced by a comprehensive service folder included with the sale. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger door that are only visible upon close inspection. Inside, the black NuLuxe interior is in excellent shape; the seats are firm and free of cracks, and the cabin remains smoke-free and fresh. All technological features, including the navigation system, premium audio, and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs quietly and smoothly, having recently undergone a full inspection and oil service. The tires have approximately 80% tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This is a solid, reliable vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of comfortable driving.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
